/2025/01/bright-eyes-fender@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bright-eyes-fender@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bright-eyes-fender@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/bright-eyes-fender@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/nos-alive">NOS Alive</a>已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bright-eyes">Bright Eyes</a>已加入 2025 年阵容。下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-people-watching-tour-live-review-3819114">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender) 住在利兹：一代乔迪明星安全进入新时代</a></strong></li></ul><p>该活动将于 7 月 10 日至 12 日在里斯本举行，2025 年的活动将标志着该节日的第 17 届。</p><p>第一波艺术家于 11 月得到确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-confirmed-as-first-headliner-nos-alive-2025-3811536">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 被任命为 2025 年第一位确认的头条人物</a>。其他知名艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">Girl In Red</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">Noah Kahan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">Benson Boone</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amyl-and-the-sniffers">Amyl And The Sniffers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 。</p><p>随后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">《Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">《Finneas》</a> 、《Dead Poet Society》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foster-the-people">《Foster The People》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/barry-cant-swim-finneas-new-names-nos-alive-2025-line-up-buy-tickets-3823960">也得到证实</a>。</p><p>现在，在音乐节的最新消息中，已经确认乔迪歌手、词曲作者和吉他手萨姆·芬德也将被添加到该法案中。他将于 7 月 11 日在葡萄牙音乐节 NOS 主舞台上首次亮相。</p><p>他的名字被添加到阵容中之际，他目前正准备发行他备受期待的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-new-single-people-watching-and-teases-album-news-3810920">第三张专辑《People Watching》。</a>它定于 2 月 21 日通过 Polydor 分享，您可以<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812917" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812917" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3812917 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812917" class="wp-caption-text">萨姆·芬德。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>该唱片于 11 月首次发布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sam-fenders-euphoric-and-hopeful-new-single-people-watching-3812916">主打歌为“People Watching”</a> ，Fender 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priority-tickets-sam-fender-uk-stadium-tour-available-now-3816107">宣布了今年夏天一些大型英国体育场演出的细节</a>。</p><p>第二位确认参加 NOS Alive 2025 的新艺术家是美国独立摇滚三人组 Bright Eyes。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/conor-oberst">康纳·奥伯斯特</a>等人他们将于 7 月 12 日在喜力舞台上首次亮相音乐节。</p><p>对于 Bright Eyes 来说，这一消息是在他们去年分享了第十张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-announce-new-album-five-dice-all-threes-with-single-bells-whistles-and-uk-and-european-tour-3768595">“Five Dice, All Threes”</a>的详细信息之后发布的。</p><p>在下面查找迄今为止最新的阵容，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fnos-alive-tickets%2Fartist%2F2045437" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><h2><strong>到目前为止，NOS Alive 2025 的阵容是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>7月10日</strong><br /><strong>奥利维亚·罗德里戈：NOS 舞台</strong><br /><strong>诺亚·卡汉：NOS 舞台</strong><br /><strong>本森·布恩：NOS 舞台</strong><br /><strong>马克·安博尔：NOS 舞台</strong><br /><strong>玻璃动物：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>巴里不会游泳：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>阿尔特玛斯：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>帕罗夫·斯特拉尔：喜力舞台</strong></p><p><strong>7月11日</strong><br /><strong>红衣少女：NOS舞台</strong><br /><strong>Sam Fender：NOS 舞台 [新公告]</strong><br /><strong>泰斯基兄弟：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>圣文森特：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>FINNEAS：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>妈妈妈妈：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>Sammy Virji：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>后座恋人：喜力舞台</strong></p><p><strong>7月12日</strong><br /><strong>莱昂之王：NOS 舞台</strong><br /><strong>培养人才：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>艾米尔和嗅探者：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>CMAT：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>未来岛屿：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>死亡诗社：喜力舞台</strong><br /><strong>明亮的眼睛：喜力舞台 [新公告]</strong></p><p> NOS Alive 2024 见证了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sum-41">Sum 41</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>等乐队的表演。</p><p>对于 Sam Fender 来说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-music-with-the-war-on-drugs-adam-granduciel-3601247">自去年 3 月以来，他一直在暗示新音乐的发布。</a>然后，十月 Fender 确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-album-is-finished-and-mastered-3799886">新专辑已经完成并“掌握”</a> 。</p><p> 《People Watching》将是他自 2021 年第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">《Seventeen Going Under》</a>以来的第一张唱片，由 Fender 与他的乐队成员 Dean Thompson 和 Joe Atkinson、制作人 Markus Dravs 和<a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/the-war-on-drugs">The War On Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 一起制作。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814935" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814935" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814935" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender.-CREDIT_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814935" class="wp-caption-text">萨姆·芬德。图片来源：马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>他前面提到的英国头条演出将于 6 月 6 日在伦敦体育场以他有史以来规模最大的演出拉开帷幕，然后于 6 月 12 日、14 日和 15 日在家乡纽卡斯尔的圣詹姆斯公园继续演出。对于后者，这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-live-in-newcastle-setlist-photos-3454626">演奏了同样的曲目2023 年可容纳 52,000 人的场馆</a>。即将到来的三场演出将意味着他打破了在圣詹姆斯公园举行的最多头条演出的记录——这一头衔之前由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>保持。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sam-fender-tickets/artist/5242347?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=SY-1cEVm7xyKUYQxaA2JC0TpUksx0%3AQDx2Cb2s0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-people-watching-tour-live-review-3819114">Fender 在利兹举行的音乐会获得了<em>NME</em>的四星评价</a>，其中写道：“曲目列表没有发生彻底的改变，而是一种自信感，可以加倍努力，采取一种对他很有帮助的可靠方法。” 。</p><p> “虽然今晚确认‘人物观察’材料必须争夺自己的地位，但新旧的成功平衡可能会将萨姆·芬德的职业生涯提升到前所未有的高度。<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">格拉斯顿伯里</a>，有人吗？</p><p>对于 Bright Eyes 来说，自从这支美国独立摇滚乐队宣布因主唱 Conor Oberst 失声而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bright-eyes-cancel-all-remaining-tour-dates-for-2024-3797920">取消 2024 年所有演出</a>以来，他们将在 NOS Alive 演出，这是他们首次确认的演出之一。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nos-alive-adds-sam-fender-and-bright-eyes-to-2025-line-up-3829830">《NOS Alive》将 Sam Fender 和 Bright Eyes 添加到 2025 年阵容中，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
卡梅隆·迪亚兹不想再拍浪漫喜剧了https://www.nme.com/news/film/cameron-diaz-doesnt-want-to-do-any-more-rom-coms-3829829?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cameron-diaz-doesnt-want-待办事项 ROM comVictoria Luxford Fri, 17 Jan 2025 10:09:23 +0000 Film NewsNewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3829829 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="卡梅隆迪亚兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我保留不再拍电影的权利”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cameron-diaz-doesnt-want-to-do-any-more-rom-coms-3829829">卡梅隆迪亚兹不想再拍浪漫喜剧</a>的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="卡梅隆迪亚兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Cameron-Diaz-Premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/charlies-angels"><em>《查理的天使》</em></a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cameron-diaz">卡梅隆·迪亚兹</a>透露，十年来首次重返好莱坞后，她不会再回归的类型是浪漫喜剧。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-are-the-best-reviewed-romcoms-of-all-time-3397751">这些是有史以来最受好评的浪漫喜剧</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员是 90 年代和 00 年代最受瞩目的明星之一，她最热门的作品是浪漫喜剧，例如<em>《玛丽有情》</em> 、 <em>《我最好朋友的婚礼</em>》和<em>《假期》</em> 。 2014 年拍摄<em>《安妮》</em>后，她开始暂停电影制作，三年后确认退休，因为她专注于家庭。</p><p>她凭借与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-foxx">杰米·福克斯</a>联合主演的动作喜剧片<em>《Back In Action》</em>重返电影界。两人扮演前中央情报局间谍，身份曝光后又重新投入工作。尽管这次复出，迪亚兹在接受采访时表示，她将对未来的角色进行选择性。</p><p> “我不知道我如何看待它。这很难说，”她告诉<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/cameron-diaz-on-her-return-to-acting-no-more-romcoms-only-momcoms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>帝国杂志</em></a>。 “如果我这么说的话，事情就会变成这样。我保留对再次拍电影说不的权利，如果我决定的话，我也保留说是的权利。我没有定义任何东西。在任何特定时刻，我都会对任何对我和我的家人有意义的事情持开放态度。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="重返行动|杰米·福克斯、卡梅隆·迪亚茨 |官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MV2nYw6gL_w?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她肯定会拒绝的一种类型是浪漫喜剧，后来在采访中说道：“不再是浪漫喜剧，只有妈妈喜剧”。</p><p>这位演员和她的丈夫、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/good-charlotte">好夏洛特</a>音乐家本吉·马登育有两个孩子。她的最后一部浪漫喜剧电影是在 2014 年主演的<em>《安妮》</em>之前不久的<em>《另一个女人》。</em></p><p> <em>《重返行动》</em>现已在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>上播出。去年，她谈到了退出演艺圈的原因，她说： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cameron-diaz-explains-why-she-left-acting-for-11-years-3803587">“感觉就像我必须做一些事情才能重新开始自己的生活”。</a>回归后，她已经确认了她最票房成功之一的续集，第五部<em>《怪物史莱克</em>》电影已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/shrek-5-set-for-2026-mike-myers-cameron-diaz-and-eddie-murphy-to-return-3773420">，原班演员全部回归</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cameron-diaz-doesnt-want-to-do-any-more-rom-coms-3829829">卡梅隆迪亚兹不想再拍浪漫喜剧</a>的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
